+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%96%B9%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%96%B9%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%96%B9%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%96%B9%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%96%B9%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%96%B9%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score | archive-date=2020-06-07 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並簽約為華星旗下歌手，為期七年{{noteTag |name=守下留情1}}。1984年再於「第二屆香港新人歌唱大賽」獲得冠軍。

